message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which holds immense value for me due to its unique features and benefits. Considering its exceptional quality and functionality, I believe it's worth more than its face value. I am offering this product to you for $125, which I think strikes a fair balance between the value I place on it and what you might consider its worth. This opportunity won't last long, so I encourage you to make a decision soon. Thank you for considering my offer.
